# Line endings
#
# `core.autocrlf=true` (common on Windows) rewrites LF -> CRLF on checkout,
# which breaks bash scripts under Git Bash / MSYS — e.g.
#   build-win-release.sh: line 19: set: pipefail: invalid option name
# The rules below override autocrlf so Unix scripts always check out as LF.
*.sh            text eol=lf
*.bash          text eol=lf
.gitattributes  text eol=lf
